These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, ritmeester, bongani
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | bongani | aristoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, spinach, apple
1. the person eating apple is on the far right##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Food   | cherry | spinach | apple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
City: marseilles, miami, rome
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| City   | marseilles | miami | rome |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
