.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, jet-ski, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Transport   | quad-bike | motorbike | jet-ski |

